How to create the first application. with Node.js

01-Configure the server by creating the file: "server.js"
02-Open the terminal and CD ~to the folder with the "server.js" file
03-Run the server by typing on therminal: node server.js
	you will not get response, server is runing 
04-Confirm server is runing by:
	a) open browser
	b) type localhost:8000
	c) make sure that you got the message from the server. 
05-Stop the server by typing on the terminal: Ctrl = C

Project done, congratulations. 
that was your first App in Node.js. 
